Problem:
Prove that $$\overrightarrow{BC} \cdot \overrightarrow{AD}\ +\ \overrightarrow{CA} \cdot \overrightarrow{BD}\ +\ \overrightarrow{AB} \cdot \overrightarrow{CD}\ = 0$$ holds for any four points $A, B, C, D \in \mathbb{R}^3$.
